[30;1m21 | [0m[35m  * This module provides SVD decomposition for matrices (both real and complex).[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35m  * Two decomposition algorithms are provided:[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35m  *  - JacobiSVD implementing two-sided Jacobi iterations is numerically very accurate, fast for sma[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m  *  - BDCSVD implementing a recursive divide & conquer strategy on top of an upper-bidiagonalizatio[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35m  * These decompositions are accessible via the respective classes and following MatrixBase methods:[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35m  *  - MatrixBase::jacobiSvd()[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35m  *  - MatrixBase::bdcSvd()[0m
